{"tid":849611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"早幾個鐘前元朗有個女仔跪曬地咁","createTime":"2018-10-05T20:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T17:56:25.000Z","uid":208722,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d43f1919b74af5efbf81f4395ba789aabf26c195","tid":849611,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:06:34.000Z","msg":"早幾個鐘前去嘉城附近間惠康買日用品，行過臭坑渠附近，見到有個女仔跪喺地，隻手拖住個冇乜反應，完全冇正視過個女仔嘅男朋友。個女仔一路喊，一路講「我乜都畀曬你，點解你重要咁對我吖？」但佢條仔依舊故我，眼尾都冇睄下個女仔。<br />\n<br />\n其實聽到個女仔歇斯底里咁喊嗰陣有少少心罨，何必咁樣作賤自己，又跪又哎咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望唔好做咩傻事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103780551d618f40fab3de0f5ba2e745f7615379","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:23:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fbba16f74a00f5ba72042fd530186a1d15e76a4","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aeeb29819617232246ddbcfbcc3789309c9893f8","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"032b61ae82bb843cf30e74d15212301ac88b74c4","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b33509203c6ee688e8dc5e6b753064df0fcb5e11","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:26:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95cadf01e42526dea222625572cdd049ef7b0844","tid":849611,"uid":189581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fbba16f74a00f5ba72042fd530186a1d15e76a4","tid":849611,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T20:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a669530